# Messy Code And Macro

This page keeps fixed macro IDs for stability and adds code, preformatted text, macro links, invalid-looking text outside code, and table content.

```javascript

function messy(value) {
  const literal = '/display/CX/DoNotParseFromCode';
  const xml = '<node attr="value">text</node>';
  return value && value.trim();
}

```

